      "message": "log: expose -logratelimit option\n\nThe existing `-logratelimit` option can disable log rate limiting, but it is hidden from ordinary help because it is registered as `DEBUG_ONLY`.\n\nExpose it in normal help so users affected by log suppression can discover the supported runtime knob, and add argsman coverage for the registered flags and help text.",
